97
00:03:30,549 --> 00:03:35,090
At first, I may feel a bit angry when somebody
talks

98
00:03:35,090 --> 00:03:39,830
some bad things about your mother countries.

99
00:03:39,830 --> 00:03:46,340
Yeah, maybe I want to argue with him and ask
him

