good things in China.

102
00:03:56,269 --> 00:04:11,180
Some people will say something about Tibet
and Xinjiang problems—like this.

103
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:20,900
And kind of, we often think that you shouldn't
have bring up such ideas.

104
00:04:20,900 --> 00:04:23,780
I think many people love China.

105
00:04:23,780 --> 00:04:27,030
Yeah, but to understand, they say something
bad on China,

106
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:30,540
I think if they're right, I think it's okay.

107
00:04:30,540 --> 00:04:31,540
It's okay?!

108
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:32,540
Yeah.

109
00:04:32,540 --> 00:04:35,880
I think if it’s a fact, you can talk something
bad

