111
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:46,200
I think better say some good thing to them.

112
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:50,020
Let them know China is a good country.

113
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:50,640
Yeah.

114
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:52,080
Ahh youth.

